{"tid":1588121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如大家做多少少去宣傳我地嘅行動目的！！","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T16:35:05.000Z","uid":13300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f61f7b2d960d3b5c39ab5a46489cfffefce7f229","tid":1588121,"uid":13300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"我阿叔問我: &ldquo;爆乜撚野商場呀????&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587925\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587925</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢個post有感而發<br />\n<br />\n小弟有個諗法就係當手足做緊一啲突發/特別（如獅鳥/玩党鐵/商場）嘅行為時，可能大家叫下口號去宣傳或解釋我地嘅出發點，去比其他人理解。希望一啲和理非或者冇咁勇敢嘅手足喺側邊大叫！！<br />\n<br />\n拋磚：<br />\n警黑勾結 為民除害<br />\n港鐵封站 危害/影響市民<br />\n  <br />\n希望大家比下意見執到更精而簡 <br />\n利申：第一次開post 屌細力啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9f0ec90717b2d4c62ae94808272ecbe7228731a4","tid":1588121,"uid":13300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"a63ef74293dd82487e380a5df67eaaed297abe05","tid":1588121,"uid":13300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e6ccc39f7c992b7188f5021ce05ae76fe2344743","tid":1588121,"uid":13300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ad03127ae19fcd3188cab609c82f2334940f890b","tid":1588121,"uid":13300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"74c5e230c7ee82f7ab599ea9c9b1317eeb24b07f","tid":1588121,"uid":13300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"5ce4fdbbfc5f43bfca61c90f85f4b89ec05f918a","tid":1588121,"uid":13300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:30:02.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"0addbb333975c8d5af4c1e3ca37d1b7eff530ff1","tid":1588121,"uid":13300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor